        {
          "username": "zhaoping zhu",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "110233727913091347509",
          "user_review_count": 1,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ260rRBf7OgAavK5dFdM_WxumLJn2HzZrIFnwDb_lr3iEYaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I\u2019ve been seeing Mandy for cleanings for a few years now, and I honestly can\u2019t recommend her enough. When I first came in, my gums were in pretty bad shape. I used to have a lot of bleeding during cleanings, and I assumed it was just genetic since both my parents have the same issue. But with Mandy\u2019s gentle, consistent care, and her helpful tips, my gums have improved so much. Now, cleanings are painless and there\u2019s barely any bleeding. Mandy is always incredibly thorough. She takes her time, explains everything clearly, and makes me feel totally at ease.\n\nDr. Rydstrom is genuine and never pushy. He checks in on my previous dental work and keeps me informed, but has never tried to sell me on unnecessary treatment. I really appreciate that.\n\nThe front desk is very friendly and super accommodating when it comes to scheduling.\n\nI don\u2019t usually write reviews, but I\u2019m genuinely grateful for the care I\u2019ve received here. They helped me realize I don\u2019t have to accept \u201cbad gums\u201d as something I just inherited.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oTFFqUlRibkJrTkZObE1YQmxSRXBJVWxCeWFuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x359369c352256e35!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmhLQjRTbnBkNFNlMXBlREpIUlByanc%7C%7C?hl=en",
